#. <section class="sutta" id="sn55.30"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn55.30:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 55"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 55"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.30:0.2"
msgid "3. Saraṇānivagga"
msgstr "3. About Sarakāni"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 30. Nandakalicchavisutta → nandakasuttaṃ (bj) | licchavi or nandaka (pts1)
msgctxt "sn55.30:0.3"
msgid "30. Nandakalicchavisutta"
msgstr "30. With Nandaka the Licchavi"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.30:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā vesāliyaṃ viharati mahāvane kūṭāgārasālāyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Vesālī, at the Great Wood, in the "
"hall with the peaked roof."

msgctxt "sn55.30:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho nandako licchavimahāmatto yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho nandakaṃ "
"licchavimahāmattaṃ bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Nandaka the Licchavi minister went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat "
"down to one side. The Buddha said to him:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.390"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.30:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Catūhi kho, nandaka, dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako sotāpanno hoti "
"avinipātadhammo niyato sambodhiparāyaṇo."
msgstr ""
"“Nandaka, a noble disciple who has four things is a stream-enterer, not "
"liable to be reborn in the underworld, bound for awakening."

msgctxt "sn55.30:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn55.30:2.3"
msgid "Idha, nandaka, ariyasāvako buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgato hoti—"
msgstr "It’s when a noble disciple has experiential confidence in the Buddha …"

msgctxt "sn55.30:2.4"
msgid "itipi so bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn55.30:2.5"
msgid "Dhamme … pe …"
msgstr "the teaching …"

msgctxt "sn55.30:2.6"
msgid "saṅghe … pe …"
msgstr "the Saṅgha …"

msgctxt "sn55.30:2.7"
msgid ""
"ariyakantehi sīlehi samannāgato hoti akhaṇḍehi … pe … samādhisaṃvattanikehi."
msgstr ""
"And they have the ethical conduct loved by the noble ones … leading to "
"immersion."

msgctxt "sn55.30:2.8"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, nandaka, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako sotāpanno hoti "
"avinipātadhammo niyato sambodhiparāyaṇo."
msgstr ""
"A noble disciple who has these four things is a stream-enterer, not liable "
"to be reborn in the underworld, bound for awakening."

# Unusual use of samyutta is not noted in dict. Here it means “bound” as in “bound for” i.e. “guaranteed”.
#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.30:3.1"
msgid ""
"Imehi ca pana, nandaka, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako āyunā "
"saṃyutto hoti dibbenapi mānusenapi;"
msgstr "A noble disciple who has these four things is guaranteed long life,"

msgctxt "sn55.30:3.2"
msgid "vaṇṇena saṃyutto hoti dibbenapi mānusenapi;"
msgstr "beauty,"

msgctxt "sn55.30:3.3"
msgid "sukhena saṃyutto hoti dibbenapi mānusenapi;"
msgstr "happiness,"

msgctxt "sn55.30:3.4"
msgid "yasena saṃyutto hoti dibbenapi mānusenapi;"
msgstr "fame,"

msgctxt "sn55.30:3.5"
msgid "ādhipateyyena saṃyutto hoti dibbenapi mānusenapi."
msgstr "and authority, both human and divine."

msgctxt "sn55.30:3.6"
msgid ""
"Taṃ kho panāhaṃ, nandaka, nāññassa samaṇassa vā brāhmaṇassa vā sutvā vadāmi. "
"Api ca yadeva mayā sāmaṃ ñātaṃ sāmaṃ diṭṭhaṃ sāmaṃ viditaṃ, tadevāhaṃ "
"vadāmī”ti."
msgstr ""
"Now, I don’t say this because I’ve heard it from some other ascetic or "
"brahmin. I only say it because I’ve known, seen, and realized it for myself.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.30:4.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, aññataro puriso nandakaṃ licchavimahāmattaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he had spoken, a certain person said to Nandaka:"

msgctxt "sn55.30:4.2"
msgid "“nahānakālo, bhante”ti."
msgstr "“Sir, it is time to bathe.”"

msgctxt "sn55.30:4.3"
msgid "“Alaṃ dāni, bhaṇe, etena bāhirena nahānena."
msgstr "“Enough now, my man, with that exterior bath."

msgctxt "sn55.30:4.4"
msgid "Alamidaṃ ajjhattaṃ nahānaṃ bhavissati, yadidaṃ—"
msgstr "This interior bathing will do for me, that is,"

msgctxt "sn55.30:4.5"
msgid "bhagavati pasādo”ti."
msgstr "confidence in the Buddha.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.30:4.6"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.30:4.7"
msgid "Saraṇānivaggo tatiyo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.30:5.1"
msgid "Mahānāmena dve vuttā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn55.30:5.2"
msgid "godhā ca saraṇā duve;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn55.30:5.3"
msgid "Duve anāthapiṇḍikā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn55.30:5.4"
msgid "duve verabhayena ca;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn55.30:5.5"
msgid "Licchavī dasamo vutto,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn55.30:5.6"
msgid "vaggo tena pavuccatīti."
msgstr ""
